title: Guitar & Bass Magazine. December 2010.
description:
Guitar & Bass Magazine. December 2010.

Guitar & Bass offers you the very best instrument reviews. 
Our product testers are all leading industry professionals 
and we've helped thousands of readers make the right choice 
about kit. And when you occasionally put down that guitar, 
there are plenty of entertaining interviews with all your 
favorite guitar hero's.

Enjoy.
